des paramètres.
	•	⏱️ Réduction du temps d’affichage sur la tablette Surveil
L’écran de confirmation affiché après avoir complété le sondage reste désormais visible seulement 3 secondes (au lieu de 8), pour fluidifier l’enchaînement des visites.
⚠️ Cette amélioration nécessite l’installation de la nouvelle version de l’application sur la tablette Surveil.

🛠️ Améliorations générales :
	•	Corrections de bugs mineurs et amélioration des performances globales de l’application.

⸻

🚀 [EN] May 15, 2025 Deployment – New Features

✨ New Features:
	•	📩 Visitor survey via Teams notification
If a visitor hasn’t completed the satisfaction survey on the tablet, a Teams notification is now sent 5 minutes after the visit is closed. The visitor can complete it from their computer or phone, with the same options as on the tablet and an optional feedback field.
This feature is disabled by default and can be enabled by managers on the Settings page.
	•	⏱️ Shorter confirmation screen on the Surveil tablet
The confirmation screen shown after submitting a survey now displays for 3 seconds instead of 8, allowing quicker turnover between visitors.
⚠️ This update requires the new version of the application to be installed on the Surveil tablet.

🛠️ General improvements:
	•	Minor bug fixes and overall performance enhancements of the application.
